    "excerpt": "The \"Prayer for North American Jews on the 75th Anniversary of Israel’s Founding\" was first published and disseminated from the website of T'ruah, via PDF <a href=\"https://truah.org/resources/prayer-for-north-american-jews-on-the-75th-anniversary-of-israels-founding/\">here</a>.  . . .",
    "content": "\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" class=\"draggable toggleable-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th id=\"x\" style=\"text-align: right;\">Source (Hebrew)</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: left;\">Translation (English)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nמְקוֹר הַחַיִּים עוֹשֶׂה פֶלֶא<br />\nבָּרֵךְ אֶת מְדִינַת יִשְׂרָאֵל<br />\nוְאֶת כׇּל תּוֹשָׁבֵי הָאָרֶץ<br />\nהָגֵן עָלֶיהָ בְּאֶבְרַת חַסְדֶּךָ<br />\nוּפְרוֹשׂ עָלֶיהָ סֻכַּת שְׁלוֹמֶךָ<br />\nחַזֵּק אֶת לִבּוֹת אֶזְרָחֶיהָ<br />\nרוֹדְפֵי הַצֶּדֶק וְהַדֵּמוֹ קְרַטְיָה<br />\nשֶׁיַּעֲבִיר וּקוֹלָם<br />\nכְּשׁוֹפָר בְּכׇל הָאָרֶץ׃\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nSource of life, Maker of wonders<br />\nbless the State of Israel<br />\nand all the inhabitants of the land.<br />\nProtect her with infinite compassion;<br />\nspread over her your shelter of peace.<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_1');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_1');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Cf. the prayer “Hashkivenu,” Cf. Amos 9:11, Cf. Rav Avraham Isaac Kook, Mo’adei HaRe’iyah (Silver from the Land of Israel) p. 97.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_1', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nStrengthen the hearts and the will of its citizens<br />\ncalling out for justice and democracy.<br />\nMay their voices ring out<br />\nlike a shofar throughout the land.<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_2');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_2');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_2\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[2]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_2\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Cf. Leviticus 25:9-10&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_2').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_2', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nצְמִיחַת גְּאֻלָּתֵנוּ<br />\nתֵּן בְּיָדָם לִנְטֹעַ מֵחָדָשׁ אֶת אֲשֶׁר נֶעֱקַר,<br />\nלְהַשְׁקוֹת אֶת אֲשֶׁר נָבַל<br />\nלְמַעַן יִפְרְחוּ וִישַׂגְשְׂגוּ שְׁתִילֵי הַבְטָחוֹת<br />\nמִקְלָט וְשִׁוְיוֹן,<br />\nאַל־תִּתֵּן לַמּוֹט רַגְלֵיהֶם,<br />\nשֶׁלֹא יָנוּמוּ וְלֹא יִישְׁנוּ בָּרֵךְ אוֹתָם׃\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nA budding redemption,<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_3');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_3');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_3\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[3]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_3\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> As in Rabbi Yitsḥak haLevi Hertzog&#8217;s &#8220;<a href=\"/?p=17652\">Prayer for the Welfare of the State of Israel</a>&#8221; (1948).&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_3').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_3', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nhelp them replant what has been uprooted<br />\nand tend what has been neglected<br />\nso the seedling promises of refuge and equality<br />\nblossom and thrive.<br />\nMay their feet not give way;<br />\nlet them not tire nor slumber nor succumb to fear.<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_4');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_4');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_4\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[4]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_4\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Cf. Psalms 121:3-4.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_4').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_4', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nחִזְקוּ וְאִמְצוּ, אַל־תִּירְאוּ<br />\nלְמַעַן עָתִיד מְשֻׁתָּף<br />\nלְכׇל מִי שֶׁהָאָרֶץ הַזֹּאת הִיא בֵּיתוֹ׃\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nGrant strength and courage<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_5');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_5');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_5\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[5]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_5\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Deuteronomy 31:6.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_5').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_5', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> &#8212;<br />\nnurture a shared future<br />\nfor all who call the land home.\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nהָרוֹפֵא לִשְׁבוּרֵי לֵב<br />\nנְצֹר אֶת תִּקְווֹתֵינוּ<br />\nעֲזֹר לָנוּ לַחְגֹּג אֶת הַנֵּס<br />\nבַּהֲקָמַת מְדִינַת יִשְׂרָאֵל<br />\nעֲזֹר לָנוּ לְהִתְאַבֵּל עַל מָה שֶׁאָבַד<br />\nבְּהַגְשָׁמַת חֲלוֹמֵנוּ׃\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nHealer of the broken-hearted,<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_6');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_6');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_6\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[6]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_6\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Psalms 147:3.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_6').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_6', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nsustain our hope.<br />\nHelp us celebrate what was and is miraculous<br />\nin Israel’s founding.<br />\nHelp us grieve all that has been lost<br />\nin the realization of that dream.\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nיְהִי רָצוֹן שֶׁנִּהְיֶה אֲמִיצִים וְכֵנִים מַסְפִּיק<br />\nלְהָכִיל אֶת הַשְּׁבָרִים בַּשָׁלֵם׃\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nMay we be strong enough and honest enough<br />\nto carry the shattered along with the whole.\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nיְהִי רָצוֹן שֶׁאַהֲבָתֵנוּ וּדְבֵקוּתֵנוּ<br />\nבַּחֲזוֹן הַנְּבִיאִים<br />\nתַּעֲמֹדְנָה כִּדְבַשׁ מִסֶּלַע<br />\nוּכְשֶׁמֶן מֵחַלְמִישׁ צוּר׃\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nMay our love and our commitment<br />\nto the vision of the Prophets<br />\nendure like honey from the crag<br />\nand oil from the flinty rock.<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_7');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_7');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_7\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[7]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_7\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Deuteronomy 32:13.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_7').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_7', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nיְהִי רָצוֹן שֶׁנִּזְכֶּה לִהְיוֹת שֻׁתָּפִים עִם אֱלֹהִים<br />\nוְעִם כׇּל תּוֹשָׁבֵיהָ אָרֶץ<br />\nלְקַיֵּם וּלְהָגֵן עַל שָׁלוֹם וְצֶדֶק וְשִׂמְחַת עוֹלָם׃\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nMay we be partners with the Divine<br />\nand with all the inhabitants of the land<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_8');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_8');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_8\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[8]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_8\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> As underscored in the State of Israel&#8217;s <a href=\"/?p=15325\">Declaration of Independence</a> (1948).&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_8').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_8', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nin establishing and protecting justice, peace and joy.\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr />\n<p>The &#8220;Prayer for North American Jews on the 75th Anniversary of Israel’s Founding&#8221; was first published and disseminated from the website of T&#8217;ruah, via PDF <a href=\"https://truah.org/resources/prayer-for-north-american-jews-on-the-75th-anniversary-of-israels-founding/\">here</a> for Yom ha-Atsma’ut in the year 2023. </p>\n<p>I have transcribed the text from the PDF, modifying the layout slightly so as to set the Hebrew phrasing side-by-side with its English translation. I have also added some missing niqud and English translation along with notation where citation references are significant. &#8211;Aharon Varady</p>\n<h3>Source(s)</h3>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"4ntUEC2X02\"><p><a href=\"https://truah.org/resources/prayer-for-north-american-jews-on-the-75th-anniversary-of-israels-founding/\">Prayer for North American Jews on the 75th Anniversary of Israel’s Founding</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" title=\"&#8220;Prayer for North American Jews on the 75th Anniversary of Israel’s Founding&#8221; &#8212; T&#039;ruah\" src=\"https://truah.org/resources/prayer-for-north-american-jews-on-the-75th-anniversary-of-israels-founding/embed/#?secret=42dGUBQ31n#?secret=4ntUEC2X02\" data-secret=\"4ntUEC2X02\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_50276\" style=\"width: 242px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Prayer-for-North-American-Jews-on-the-75th-Anniversary-of-Israels-Founding-Ayelet-Cohen-Truah-2023.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50276\" src=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Prayer-for-North-American-Jews-on-the-75th-Anniversary-of-Israels-Founding-Ayelet-Cohen-Truah-2023-232x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"232\" height=\"300\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-50276\" srcset=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Prayer-for-North-American-Jews-on-the-75th-Anniversary-of-Israels-Founding-Ayelet-Cohen-Truah-2023-232x300.png 232w, https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Prayer-for-North-American-Jews-on-the-75th-Anniversary-of-Israels-Founding-Ayelet-Cohen-Truah-2023-791x1024.png 791w, https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Prayer-for-North-American-Jews-on-the-75th-Anniversary-of-Israels-Founding-Ayelet-Cohen-Truah-2023.png 1258w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 232px) 100vw, 232px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-50276\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Prayer for North American Jews on the 75th Anniversary of Israel&#8217;s Founding (Ayelet Cohen, Truah 2023)</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"speaker-mute footnotes_reference_container\"> <div class=\"footnote_container_prepare\"><p><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_label pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_expand_collapse_reference_container__1();\">Notes</span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_collapse_button\" style=\"display: none;; display: none;\" onclick=\"footnote_expand_collapse_reference_container__1();\"></span></p></div> <div id=\"footnote_references_container__1\" style=\"\"><table class=\"footnotes_table footnote-reference-container\"><caption class=\"accessibility\">Notes</caption> <tbody> \r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >1</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Cf. the prayer “Hashkivenu,” Cf. Amos 9:11, Cf. Rav Avraham Isaac Kook, Mo’adei HaRe’iyah (Silver from the Land of Israel) p. 97.</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_2\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_2');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >2</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Cf. Leviticus 25:9-10</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_3\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_3');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >3</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">As in Rabbi Yitsḥak haLevi Hertzog&#8217;s &#8220;<a href=\"/?p=17652\">Prayer for the Welfare of the State of Israel</a>&#8221; (1948).</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_4\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_4');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >4</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Cf. Psalms 121:3-4.</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_5\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_5');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >5</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Deuteronomy 31:6.</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_6\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_6');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >6</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Psalms 147:3.</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_7\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_7');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >7</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Deuteronomy 32:13.</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_8\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_8');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >8</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">As underscored in the State of Israel&#8217;s <a href=\"/?p=15325\">Declaration of Independence</a> (1948).</td></tr>\r\n\r\n </tbody> </table> </div></div><script type=\"text/javascript\"> function footnote_expand_reference_container__1() { jQuery('#footnote_references_container__1').show(); jQuery('#footnote_reference_conta